    <item>
      <title>摩根大通和野村证券暂停交易，Segantii 事件影响扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/segantii-fallout-broadens-as-jpmorgan-nomura-hit-pause-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的迈克尔·摩尔 (Michael Moore) 告诉索纳利·巴萨克 (Sonali Basak)，在调查展开期间，摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 和野村控股 (Nomura Holdings Inc.) 限制了与这家对冲基金的交易，华尔街正在感受到 Segantii Capital Management Inc. (Segantii Capital Management Inc.) 在香港的内幕交易调查带来的涟漪。关于“彭博市场”。摩尔报告称，此次调查增加了全球有关大宗交易处理的问题。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/segantii-fallout-broadens-as-jpmorgan-nomura-hit-pause-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储库克表示私人信贷并未损害金融弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fed-s-cook-says-private-credit-hasn-t-hurt-financial-resilience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，非银行投资公司贷款的增加值得关注，但似乎并未给金融体系带来过度风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fed-s-cook-says-private-credit-hasn-t-hurt-financial-resilience</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储柯林斯：实现通胀目标可能需要更长时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/fed-s-collins-reaching-inflation-goal-may-take-longer-than-thought</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿联邦储备银行行长苏珊·柯林斯表示，最近的数据让她相信，将通胀率恢复到央行 2% 的目标将需要“比之前想象的更长的时间”。柯林斯周三在麻省理工学院发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-08/fed-s-collins-reaching-inflation-goal-may-take-longer-than-thought</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:23:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着新的自愿减产生效，俄罗斯石油产量高于目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/russia-pumps-oil-above-target-as-new-voluntary-cuts-enter-force</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社根据官方数据计算，俄罗斯上个月的原油产量削减幅度低于承诺，超过了 3 月份与 OPEC+ 达成的自愿目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/russia-pumps-oil-above-target-as-new-voluntary-cuts-enter-force</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国拍卖需求不温不火，美国国债维持日内跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/treasuries-hold-day-s-losses-as-us-auction-met-with-tepid-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国财政部出售 10 年期国债的需求略显不温不火，美国政府债务当天仍处于较低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/treasuries-hold-day-s-losses-as-us-auction-met-with-tepid-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:11:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citrix 母公司发行 15 亿美元债券，收益率为 8.25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/citrix-parent-taps-bond-market-for-third-debt-sale-in-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citrix Systems 母公司云软件集团 (Cloud Software Group) 正在六个月内第三次利用美国债务市场，因为它希望偿还更昂贵的债务，这是众多高风险借款人利用良性信贷条件筹集现金的最新例子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/citrix-parent-taps-bond-market-for-third-debt-sale-in-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长温施警告通胀前景风险持续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ecb-s-wunsch-warns-that-risks-to-inflation-outlook-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员皮埃尔·温施 (Pierre Wunsch) 仍然认为消费者价格存在危险——如果货币政策与美国分歧过大，欧元将走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ecb-s-wunsch-warns-that-risks-to-inflation-outlook-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国驱逐俄罗斯特使 抵制间谍活动激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/uk-to-expel-russian-diplomat-in-crackdown-on-alleged-spying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国驱逐了一名俄罗斯高级特使，并对该国外交官实施了新的限制，这是迄今为止对盟国官员所说的旨在削弱对乌克兰支持的协调间谍活动的最引人注目的回应之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/uk-to-expel-russian-diplomat-in-crackdown-on-alleged-spying</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 12:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于剧烈波动持续，可可期货抹去了早先的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cocoa-gains-almost-20-in-two-days-as-severe-volatility-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国可可期货几乎回吐了周三早些时候的全部涨幅，在过去两天价格飙升 20% 的反弹之后，对冲基金退出了看涨押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cocoa-gains-almost-20-in-two-days-as-severe-volatility-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
